                      ),
                    ),
                  ),
                ),
                const SizedBox(width: 8),
                // ComboBox Trier par
                Expanded(
                  flex: 1,
                  child: InkWell(
                    onTap: () {
                      final RenderBox button = context.findRenderObject() as RenderBox;
                      final RenderBox overlay = Navigator.of(context).overlay!.context.findRenderObject() as RenderBox;
